ation specialists have a 98% approval rate across all visa categories."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How much does tax filing cost in Atlanta?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Our Atlanta tax preparation services start at $149 for simple individual returns (1040). Business returns, multi-state filings, and complex returns are quoted after a free consultation. We offer flat-fee pricing — no hourly billing, no hidden charges."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you handle IRS audits for Atlanta clients?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Our IRS-enrolled agents are authorized to represent clients directly before the IRS in all audit, collection, and appeals matters. Every return we file includes year-round audit support at no additional charge."}}]}a:["$","$1","c",{"children":[[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$f"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://goldendollarconsulting.com\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Locations\",\"item\":\"https://goldendollarconsulting.com/locations\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Atlanta, GA\",\"item\":\"https://goldendollarconsulting.com/locations/atlanta-ga\"}]}"}}],["$","script","2",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}]],"$L11","$L12"],null,"$L13"]}]
